Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就是…維甘的基地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.39,0:00:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是維甘的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.21,0:01:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎 來到維甘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.48,0:03:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陌生的景象 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你不喜歡和敵人對話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 這裏就是火星圈最大的衛星殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮二號
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.36,0:03:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是那些被遺忘者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷著堅強的信念 建起的維甘的象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了奪回地球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我力求建立最強大的軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論技術 士氣 軍隊向心力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.79,0:03:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無一不是頂級水準
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群被遺忘在火星的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何能擁有這樣的軍事力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經一切準備就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會負責收押俘虜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒有那個必要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他暫時留在我這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的身份略顯特殊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進展如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在分析
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正在EXA-DB中搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對設計製造新型高達有幫助的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型高達？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人告訴您嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運用維甘的最新技術
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設計製造新型高達
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是伊澤爾坎特大人的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達也是能憑空造出來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EXA-DB 實在超乎想像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那是舊國家戰爭時代的遺產
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被禁止的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭本身雖然愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但諷刺的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科技卻會因此迅猛發展
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說在那個時代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是一台最普通的機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也遠非現在可比
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而一位機師 則可以同時操縱幾百台部件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至駕駛集戰爭技術於一身的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大規模殺傷性武器橫行戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們發現的還只是其中的極小一部分？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 正是這部分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形成了維甘的現代技術基礎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.39,0:05:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦獲得全部技術遺產會如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以實現的話 這場戰爭就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會宣告結束嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天祐我維甘！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被詛咒的秘寶 EXA-DB
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這裏就可以 退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你就是那位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在地球圈抓到的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這孩子難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的眼神對你沒有任何好處
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一聲令下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾秒鐘後 你就會成為一具死屍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底打算帶我來這裏幹什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於張口說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會作為地球圈的代表見證這裏的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見證維甘的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過今天旅途勞頓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經為你準備了房間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.48,0:06:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我負責照顧你 請叫我瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顧我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了 就是這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 所以才會被允許使用這間房間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這張臉 簡直像極了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是伊澤爾坎特大人的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說好久以前就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.69,0:07:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪會給你特別待遇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則俘虜一般住不上這樣的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.82,0:08:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 把身上的衣服脫下來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換新衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要帶我上哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.67,0:08:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我們為何要向地球聯邦發動戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中的真正原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是為了侵略地球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侵略地球？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是侵略 而是奪回
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們發誓不惜任何手段要重返地球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並奪回作為人的尊嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.68,0:08:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你們殺了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論有什麼理由都不能這麼做！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能夠體會到嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被宣告「死刑」的人們的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「火星圈」「夢想中的新天地」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那不過都是幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗的星球改造和磁力風暴所引發的不治之癥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使那裏淪為一片死病蔓延之地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星圈的人們在與病魔的鬥爭中繁衍生息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,編織起了屬於他們的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.19,0:09:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終有一天要重返地球家園！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將這個心願深埋心中 生存了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們選擇戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為奪回這片名為地球的故土
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我們戰鬥的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能夠體會到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 就算這樣 維甘也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.04,0:09:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ID卡和聯絡用終端
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.18,0:10:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以在城市中和我們取得聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者購買必需品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.34,0:10:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是你的目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必擔心 過後會來接你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 去瞭解一下維甘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去親眼看看自己恨之入骨的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人真正的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.13,0:10:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有醜話說在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你時刻受到監視
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做無謂的嘗試
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.31,0:11:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說過多少次了 不要再幹這種事！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.42,0:12:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是這裏的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.85,0:12:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒用 不過就是點擦傷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我家 不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是小心點為好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.22,0:12:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近不太平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家活得都挺難的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被逼得走投無路了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去床上躺著！露烏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.90,0:12:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我叫吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我叫露烏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你受傷了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不過沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫狄恩 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～看起來不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.30,0:13:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 一起吃頓飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和你聊聊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露烏！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想聽聽外面的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼先告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐是從哪來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有點…遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在上學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼樣的學校 教些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐擅長什麼體育項目？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.74,0:14:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羨慕吉歐 我也好想去上學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家聊聊天 有時還吵嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一定很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒上過學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該知道 這種病需要臥床
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不治之癥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.10,0:14:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊澤爾坎特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個少年是高達的機師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.13,0:14:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不應該審訊他 從他嘴裏收集情報嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有到那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 時不我待啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.72,0:14:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有我的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說說吧 你們那邊怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們那邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是問你 你們衛星上的病情控制怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想說的話 那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經 活不長了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.04,0:15:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最多還有三個月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太不公平了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹她做錯了什麼非要死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的病 這麼重嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以想想辦法呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想辦法？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便有藥 也不可能照顧到我們這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不可能完全治好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是多活一段時間而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.91,0:15:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球上的傢伙們在安全的地方享福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們卻被迫過著這種生活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太自私了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.02,0:15:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:15:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊澤爾坎特大人總有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會把我們帶回地球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.24,0:16:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想去看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.91,0:16:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒有 看到妹妹那麼開心過了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.93,0:16:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好不要再來找我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的成了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對她來說 只有痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.45,0:16:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不可以來找我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己的身體 自己最清楚！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露烏！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…就算這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看看更多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看看更多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.61,0:17:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不明白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算去更多的地方 認識更多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離別馬上就會到來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會徒增傷感…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得害怕迎接死亡…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我寧願那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧願最後變成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想活得像個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想活得像個人那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想和吉歐聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多事想問吉歐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:18:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親眼見證火星圈的現狀後有何感想？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.95,0:18:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們總是為心愛的人著想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渴望從家庭中獲得溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在這裏 如此單純的願望也會遭到踐踏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.14,0:18:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘的人們因害怕失去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而刻意壓制著感情生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 狄恩他們是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.19,0:18:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你遇到的那個少年的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實大家小的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都保留有一份人類的感性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.19,0:18:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 隨著長大成人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.51,0:18:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便失去了那份愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不再執著於家人和戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕全心全意的去愛別人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽得見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們因為不願被奪走情感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.51,0:18:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而發出的吶喊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們並非為死亡而悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是為不能活得像個正常人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.33,0:18:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而傷心欲絕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真正的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是一場簡單的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在之前的每一次戰鬥中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都為你們提供了倖存的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對那些渾渾噩噩的地球種們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我始終都在向他們發問
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.89,0:19:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否有生存的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.37,0:19:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否有生存的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法理解！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊澤爾坎特大人對那位少年太缺乏戒心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是個孩子 畢竟是敵人的機師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得放鬆監視
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.46,0:19:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如有萬一 由我們親手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要那個少年的命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的 今天我又把那孩子錯看成了羅米
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.69,0:20:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是命運的捉弄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,診斷如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.89,0:20:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生說了 剩餘時間不足六個月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.18,0:20:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須堅持
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還要親手打開通往伊甸的大門
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 這是我們活到今天的目的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.74,0:20:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從失去羅米的那天開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離別馬上就會到來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.40,0:20:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會變得害怕迎接死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.66,0:20:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我寧願那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧願最後變成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:21:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想活得像個人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想活得像個人那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎 吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.10,0:21:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們並非為死亡而悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是為不能活得像個正常人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而傷心欲絕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們捕獲高達
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功阻止了聯邦增強戰鬥力的企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸計劃開始進入最終階段
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.91,0:21:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時機來臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為這一天賭上了全部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得嗎 傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次告訴你這項計劃的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下從未有一天忘記過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.52,0:21:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為奪回作為人的尊嚴和權利
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.13,0:21:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是這份崇高的志向
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.17,0:21:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指引我戰鬥到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.07,0:21:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.45,0:22:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 伊澤爾坎特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.20,0:22:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 馬上進入零部件的高速成型工序
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.75,0:22:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誕生自維甘的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.64,0:22:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的高達
